<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10144835>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Phylogenetic reconstruction of the relationships of different Cabdio species based on the Maximum likelihood and Bayesian analysis of the mitochondrial DNA barcode region. Numbers near nodes are UFBoot/SH-aLRT/Posterior Probability values. The tree is drawn to scale with branch lengths depicting number of substitutions per site. The list of sequences is presented in Table 1." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10144835/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10144843>
